# Marketing (Astro) Agent Guidelines

- Treat `apps/template/marketing` as the source template for landing/blog sites.
- Keep output static-first and SEO-friendly; default to Astro pages and content collections.
- Reuse `@yca-software/design-system` marketing components before creating app-local variants.
- Keep content authoring in `src/content/blog/*.md` with frontmatter (`title`, `summary`, `publishedAt`, `tags`, `draft`).
- Keep metadata centralized via `src/components/SeoHead.astro` and apply canonical URLs.
- Keep app-specific identity changes minimal and consistent (name, copy, contact info, env values).
- If adding env vars, update `.env.example` and template docs in the same change.
